*kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4-r1 (18 Sep 2006)

  18 Sep 2006; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org>
  +kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Disable broken tests. Fix KDE bug #106648 and a few minor issues. Fix bug
  #146648.

  17 Sep 2006; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org>
  -kdebase-kioslaves-3.4.3.ebuild:
  Drop KDE 3.4.

  08 Sep 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4.ebuild:
  Accept dbus-qt3-old aside from dbus proper, and don't do the useflag check
  for that case.

  03 Sep 2006; Bryan Østergaard <kloeri@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Stable on ia64.

  02 Aug 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4-dbuscrash.patch,
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4.ebuild:
  Add a patch to fix crashes when D-Bus is not started, thanks to Tobias
  Powalowski from Archlinux.

  01 Aug 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4.ebuild:
  Require kdialog 3.5.4.

*kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4 (25 Jul 2006)

  25 Jul 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.4.ebuild:
  Bump to 3.5.4 (pre-release).

  22 Jun 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.4.3.ebuild:
  Move myconf population in src_compile rather than global scope.

  22 Jun 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.2.ebuild, kdebase-kioslaves-3.5.3.ebuild:
  Add check for qt3 bindings in dbus when HAL support is enabled, thanks to
  Rickard Närström in bug #137551. Move myconf population in src_compile
  rather than global scope.

